Item 2. Properties.
JPMorgan Chase’s headquarters is located in New York City at 383
Madison Avenue, a 47-story office building that it owns. The Firm has
commenced a project to demolish its former headquarters at 270 Park
Avenue in New York City and to build a new headquarters on the same
site.
