predominantly into the Firm’s investment-related products. The
decrease in CB was driven by a reduction in non-operating
deposits. The decrease in Corporate was predominantly due to
maturities of wholesale non-operating deposits, consistent with the
Firm’s efforts to reduce such deposits.
