The Firm’s loan portfolio is divided into three portfolio segments, which are the same segments used by the Firm to determine the allowance for
loan losses: Consumer, excluding credit card; Credit card; and Wholesale. Within each portfolio segment the Firm monitors and assesses the credit
risk in the following classes of loans, based on the risk characteristics of each loan class.
