Consumer , excluding cr edit card, loan portfolio
Consumer loans, excluding credit card loans, consist primarily of
residential mortgages, home equity loans and lines of credit, auto loans
and consumer and business banking loans, with a focus on serving the
prime consumer credit market. The portfolio also includes home equity
loans secured by junior liens, prime mortgage loans with an interest-
only payment period, and certain payment-option loans that may result
in negative amortization.
